## 📁 Project Structure

```
multi-agent-code-review/
├── main.py                        # Entry point
├── config.py                      # Configuration (output dir, settings)
├── requirements.txt               # Dependencies
├── .env                           # API keys (not committed)
├── output/                        # Generated reports
│   ├── report.json
│   └── report.md
└── research_system/
    ├── __init__.py
    ├── core/
    │   ├── __init__.py
    │   ├── file_scanner.py        # Scans and reads codebase files
    │   ├── graph.py               # LangGraph agent graph definition
    │   └── state.py               # Shared state between agents
    └── agents/
        ├── __init__.py
        ├── security_agent.py      # Security vulnerability detection
        ├── architecture_agent.py  # Architecture analysis
        ├── code_quality_agent.py  # Code quality analysis
        └── reporter.py            # Aggregates findings into report
```

