## 📋 Severity Levels

| Level | Description |
|-------|-------------|
| 🔴 **Critical** | Immediate security risk, must fix now |
| 🟠 **High** | Serious issue, fix before production |
| 🟡 **Medium** | Should be addressed soon |
| 🟢 **Low** | Minor improvements suggested |
| ℹ️ **Info** | Informational observations |

